title: Ques Disabled
body: Are the ques for everything but Aram and Blind pick suppose to be down? I am unable to play any ranked que, super bummed.

replies.body: I don't see any issues with playing ranked matches currently.  Are you still seeing any issues?
I've seen this posted multiple times on reddit today. The people having this issue had to relog once or twice and apparently it worked for them.
An odd thing, and I wonder if it's happening on either or both versions of the client.  I'll keep an eye out, thanks for the heads up.  :D
It affected me on both my computers but literally hours later (probably when you saw it), they were working again.
I'm having the same issue, but my buddy is able to queue up just fine. I don't get it.
